[I] USB CCID (Chip/Smart Card Interface Devices) and ICCD (Integrated Circuit(s) Card Devices) drivers

[T] This package provides the source code for a generic USB CCID (Chip/Smart
[T] Card Interface Devices) driver and ICCD (Integrated Circuit(s) Card
[T] Devices).

